Bitcoin Trezor Plugin
=====================

Manual installation:

  1) install udev rule definition
     * copy trezor-udev.rules to /usr/lib/udev/rules.d/51-trezor-udev.rules

  2a) install plugin (32-bit Linux)
      * copy file npBitcoinTrezorPlugin.32bit.so to your browsers plugin directory
        - the directory usually is /usr/lib/mozilla/plugins or /usr/lib/browser-plugins

  2b) install plugin (64-bit Linux)
      * copy file npBitcoinTrezorPlugin.64bit.so to your browsers plugin directory
        - the directory usually is /usr/lib/mozilla/plugins or /usr/lib/browser-plugins
        - it can also be located in /usr/lib64 instead of /usr/lib
